---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/article.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ayllu - Support — jtdub.com" description="Get help with the Ayllu app. Find answers to common questions, report issues, and request features.">
  <article class="article">
    <div class="article__body" style="max-width: var(--measure); margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-9) var(--gutter) var(--space-10);">
<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1>Ayllu &mdash; Support</h1>
            <p class="lead">Offline-first field research companion for archaeological, anthropological, and ecological fieldwork.</p>

            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            <p class="text-muted">This app is currently in development. FAQs will be added as features are finalized.</p>

            <h2>Get Help</h2>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h5><i class="bi bi-bug me-2"></i>Report a Bug</h5>
                <p>Found something that isn't working right? Open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/jtdub/ayllu-app/issues" target="_blank">feedback repository</a> with a description of the problem.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h5><i class="bi bi-lightbulb me-2"></i>Request a Feature</h5>
                <p>Have an idea for improving Ayllu? Submit a feature request on <a href="https://github.com/jtdub/ayllu-app/issues" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h5><i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Contact the Developer</h5>
                <p>For general questions or support inquiries, visit the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="text-muted"><a href="/apps/">&#8592; Back to Apps</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
